## 🧰 Tech Stack

- **Languages:** Python, HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- **Frontend:** Web-based interface using HTML5 + JS animation
- **Backend:** Python (Flask/FastAPI)
- **APIs:** Google Speech Recognition, Google Translate, gTTS/pyttsx3, etc.
- **Libraries:** SpeechRecognition, gTTS/pyttsx3, DeepSpeech/Wav2Vec2 (optional), Flask
- **AI:** NLP translation pipeline
- **Optional Integration:** ESP32 (for IoT audio output, future scope)

